These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-1::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: drawing, reading
The people have 2 different jobs:  project-manager, journalist
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: surfing, ice-hockey
The people use 2 different means of transport: tram, train
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the far right##1
2. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the person driving the train##1
3. the project-manager is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2     |
| Hobby       | reading       | drawing |
| Job         | journalist | project-manager  |
| Sport       | ice-hockey    | surfing    |
| Transport   | train       | tram      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: tea, iced-tea
The people have 2 different jobs:  bartender, electrician
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: spy, family
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: skiing, parkour
1. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
2. the bartender is on the far left##1
3. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |
| Beverage      | iced-tea     | tea |
| Job           | bartender | electrician      |
| Movie-Genre   | family  | spy      |
| Sport         | skiing | parkour     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, hot-chocolate
There 2 different types of food: pepper, mango
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: reggae, r&b
The people use 2 different means of transport: scooter, boat
1. the fan of r&b is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
2. the person drinking almond-milk is the person driving the boat##1
3. the person eating pepper is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| Beverage      | almond-milk | hot-chocolate  |
| Food          | pepper    | mango   |
| Music-Genre   | r&b  | reggae   |
| Transport     | boat     | scooter |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-4::.
