There 2 different types of food: peach, pumpkin
The people have 2 different jobs:  project-manager, dancer
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: folk, electronic
1. the fan of folk is on the far left##1
2. the project-manager is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
3. the person drinking fanta is the person eating peach##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| Beverage      | milk       | fanta |
| Food          | pumpkin         | peach    |
| Job           | dancer | project-manager    |
| Music-Genre   | folk           | electronic   |

