2. the fan of pop is on the right of the person eating kiwi##1
3. the american is on the right of the owner of the pony##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |
| Food          | kiwi | cauliflower |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop     | pop      |
| Nationality   | chinese | american    |
| Pet           | pony    | goat    |

